<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Trésor Malagasy</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0c0d0eff,  #004aad);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out;
        }

        .hero p.slogan {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #fffbe6;
            animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease-out;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #004aad;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in;
        }

        .activities {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 30px 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .activities li {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border: 2px solid #004aad;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 250px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeInUp 2s ease;
        }

        .activities li:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .buttons {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .buttons a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #004aad;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .buttons a:hover {
            background-color: #004aad;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color:white;
            color: #000;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero">
         <img 
                src="{{ asset('uploads/profile_photos/tresor.png') }}" 
                width="120" height="120" 
                style="border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;">
        <h1>
           TRESOR MALAGASY</h1>
        <p class="slogan">"VOLA TSARA KAJY, MAHATSARA FIHAVANANA"</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
        <h2>Bienvenue sur notre plateforme</h2>
        <p>Découvrez les services offerts par le Trésor Public de Madagascar :</p>

        <ul class="activities">
            <li>Gestion des finances publiques</li>
            <li>Paiement des fonctionnaires</li>
            <li>Suivi des recettes fiscales</li>
            <li>Consultation des documents comptables</li>
            <li>Demandes et déclarations en ligne</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="{{ path('app_inscription') }}">S'inscrire</a>
            <a href="{{ path('app_connexion') }}">Se connecter</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Trésor Malagasy - Tous droits réservés.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>